## 📋 ЧЕКЛИСТ ПЕРЕД СЕССИЕЙ

- [ ] Последний блок `SESSION_HANDOFF.md`
- [ ] `STATUS.md` — фаза, gates, blockers
- [ ] `.agents/memory/MEMORY.md` — CONFIRMED_FACTS, LEARNED_RULES
- [ ] Роли и write locks (ниже) не нарушены

---

## 📐 РОЛИ И WRITE LOCKS

| Role | Model/CLI | Load | Writes | Does NOT write |
|------|-----------|------|--------|----------------|
| Orchestrator | ${ORCHESTRATOR} | ${ORCH_PCT} | STATUS, MEMORY, program SPEC/PLAN | executor evidence lanes |
| Wave Executor | ${EXECUTOR} | ${EXEC_PCT} | audits/${EXECUTOR_LANE}/, EXEC-REPORT, research/ | STATUS, MEMORY |
| Cross-auditor | ${AUDITOR} | ${AUD_PCT} | audits/${AUDITOR_LANE}/ | STATUS, MEMORY, program SPEC |
| Stateless pull | ${FLASH} | ${FLASH_PCT} | research/ (ephemeral) | STATUS, MEMORY |

Self-assessment required before locking any role ≥10% load.

---

## §1. FAILURE PACKET

При 2× одинаковой ошибке подряд:

```
ROOT CAUSE: [одна строка]
ACTION: [switch-tool | re-read-source | change-strategy | ask-user]
CLASSIFICATION: [MODEL_ERROR | ENV_ERROR | AMBIGUOUS]
```

---

## §2. HANDOFF

1. Конец сессии: append `SESSION_HANDOFF.md`
2. Факты → `.agents/memory/MEMORY.md`
3. Планы/фаза → `plan.md` / `STATUS.md` (orchestrator)
4. Не коммитить SESSION_HANDOFF.md

---

## §3. ИЕРАРХИЯ

1. AGENTS.md (этот файл)
2. SPEC.md (program architecture)
3. `.agents/rules/*`
4. plan.md / STATUS.md
5. SESSION_HANDOFF.md (оперативное)

---

## §4. АРХИТЕКТУРА

```
${PROJECT_DIR}/
├── AGENTS.md
├── SPEC.md
├── INTENT.md
├── STATUS.md
├── plan.md
├── SESSION_HANDOFF.md          # gitignored, append-only
├── .agents/memory/MEMORY.md
├── prompts/_dispatch/
├── waves/
├── audits/
├── docs/
└── research/
```

### Loaded Context

**Level 1 (always):** SESSION_HANDOFF (last block), STATUS.md, MEMORY.md  
**Level 2 (trigger):** SPEC.md, plan.md, rules/*  
**Level 3 (on-demand):** waves/*, prompts/*, audits/*, research/*

---

## §5. R.A.E.H.

```
DRAFT (wave-spec) → REVIEW* (stamp) → AGREE → EXECUTE → VERIFY → HANDOFF
```

New session per wave. Same session across review rounds. MAX_ROUNDS=5.

